Ingredients:
    Flour 400g
    Pepperoni x1
    Black Pepper 3g
    Salt 3g
    Thyme 3g
    Yeast x1
    Egg x3
    Potato x1
    Ketchup Pack x1
    Mayonnaise Pack x1
Steps:
    HAMBURGER BUN:
        Add to a Mixing Bowl and Mix with Stand Mixer
            Flour 400g
            Yeast x1
            Egg x3

        Extract from Mixing Bowl
            Hamburger Bun x4

        Transfer to a Baking Tray and Bake in Oven
    MEAT:
        Slice
            Pepperoni
        Season Pepperoni Slice with
            Thyme 3g
            Salt 3g
            Black Pepper 3g
            
        Grill
            Pepperoni Slice(Each Side)

        Slice
            Hamburger Bun(Gives HamburgerBunBottom and HamburgerBunTop)
    FRENCH FRIES:
        Slice
            Potato (Gives Potato Slices)

        Slice
            Potato Slices (Gives French Fries)

        Add to a Deep Fryer
            Sunflower Oil 0.15 lt

        Fry Using Deep Fryer
            French Fries
    Transfer to Plate
        French Fries x1
        Mayonnaise x1
        Ketchup x1 
        HamburgerBunTop x1
        HamburgerBunBottom x1
        Pepperoni Slice x1

    Serve Hot